Maintainer: Federico Cavalieri <f@28.io>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), cmake, zorba, libtidy-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://www.zorba-xquery.com

Package: zorba-html-module
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, zorba, libtidy-dev
Description: a general purpose XQuery processor
 This module provides functions to tidy a HTML document.
 The functions in this module take an HTML document (a string) as parameter,
 tidy it in order to result in valid XHTML, and return this XHTML document as a
 document-node. 
